Title: Veet Hair Removal Cream Brightening Normal to Dry(25 g)
Description: Is short and stubborn body hair making you conscious about wearing that skirt that you know you can flaunt your toned legs in? It’s not too late for you to get smooth skin. If you want to remove body hair the right way, give this Brightening Veet Hair Removal Cream a try. Smooths and brightens Enriched with microbeads, this hair removal cream, for normal to dry skin, removes dead skin cells so your skin looks brighter and feels smoother with every use. Effectively removes hair This creamy formula works its way to the hair roots, to give you a close and long-lasting shave. How To Use: Step 1 -  Evenly spread the cream on your skin, coating the hairs completely, using the curved part of the spatula. Step 2 - After 3 minutes, use the spatula to gently remove a small area of the cream to see if the hair comes off easily. If it does, remove the rest of the cream. If your hair is stubborn, you can leave the cream on for up to 6 minutes in total, not longer than that. Step 3 - Thoroughly rinse your skin with water to wash away the hair completely, and then pat dry. Precautions: 1) Please read and retain the outer packaging that has full precautions and directions for use. 2) The application time should NOT exceed 6 minutes. 3) This product is suitable for use on legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. 4) This product is NOT suitable for use on the head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples. 5) Do not use this product on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated or sunburnt skin. Avoid use if your skin has had an adverse reaction to hair removal creams in the past. 6) Please give a gap of at least 72 hours between hair removal sessions. 7) If you are taking medication which can affect skin, or if you suffer from any skin-related disorder, please consult your doctor before using this product. 8) Before e very use, test your skin’s reaction to the product by using it on a small area. If there is no adverse reaction after 24 hours, you may continue to use it. 9) If you experience any smarting/tingling sensation while using the product, remove it immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, please seek medical advice. 10) Avoid scratching the skin where the product has been used. 11) Please wait 24 hours before using antiperspirants, perfumed products and artificial tanning equipment, or swimming or sunbathing. 12) Please keep the product out of reach of children. In case of ingestion, please seek immediate medical advice and produce the outer packaging of the product. 13) The product should not come in contact with eyes, but if it does, rinse with plenty of water and seek medical advice immediately.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Body and Skin Care>Body Care>Hair Removal
